{"tid":1565392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再掛住唱歌玩人鏈啦","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:37:50.000Z","uid":87688,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4603b33fe9f1f5c657cc0a626bd44cb228def1ba","tid":1565392,"uid":87688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"做返正經野好冇？<br />\n開左學之後越黎越似14年<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人鏈玩過幾次全港大型，影過相，記錄過就夠啦...日日都搞人鏈有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n歌可以唱，但配合埋行動好冇？<br />\n<br />\n日日大合唱，唱完叫下口號拍下手又走，同14年有咩分別<br />\n過多一個月分分鐘回復原貌，等入再教育營啦大家"},{"pid":"e5faa846e325f557e70f386e5b4074a2783f498a","tid":1565392,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d42b8e1c58ae882ac8b027f787bde77b775db1d5","tid":1565392,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=bd3904a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"b17becf92f299568c2e24ed73615c581be7ef6df","tid":1565392,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZH76Gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZH76Gs.jpg&h=45845535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrSLTms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrSLTms.jpg&h=ad8f0a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T92zMGs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT92zMGs.jpg&h=fc02c1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGQhKs8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGQhKs8.png&h=e64c2b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUyfv78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUyfv78.jpg&h=31b85136&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"336df81b821e8dda12869b72